omplete and safety\u2011critical profile for long\u2011distance operations. While his communication style and professional development could be addressed through training, his proven reliability, composure, decision quality, and positive crew interaction make him the strongest overall choice.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fC\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
